### WeatherApp — CosmoApiServer
### Works with: VS Code REST Client, JetBrains Rider/IntelliJ, Visual Studio
###
### Quick start:
###   1. Start the server: dotnet run --project samples/WeatherApp
###   2. Send "Login (admin)" — copy the token from the response
###   3. Paste it into @token below
###   4. Send any other request

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@contentType = application/json

# After running Login, paste the returned token here:
@token = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..OswtgHS52Qt-6Sk9CFZ38r2UXm0kd1eeE42qoo2OHfk


### ─── AUTH ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin123"
}

###

# @name loginViewer
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "username": "viewer",
  "password": "viewer123"
}

###

# Login — invalid credentials (expect 401)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "wrongpassword"
}

###

# Get current authenticated user
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ─── WEATHER ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Get all forecasts
GET {{baseUrl}}/weather
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

# Get forecast by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/weather/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

# Get forecast by ID — not found (expect 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/weather/9999
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

# Create a new forecast
POST {{baseUrl}}/weather
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "date": "2026-06-01",
  "temperatureC": 28,
  "summary": "Sunny"
}

###

# Delete a forecast
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/weather/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

# Get all forecasts — no token (expect 401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/weather

###

### ─── SQL (mirrors Blazor test pages) ───────────────────────────────────────

# Query — stream rows as JSON (mirrors Query.razor)
# Uses sys.objects (built-in SQL Server table, always available)
GET {{baseUrl}}/sql/query?sql=SELECT TOP 100 * FROM sys.objects
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

# Query — AccountTrans table (mirrors Query.razor)
GET {{baseUrl}}/sql/query?sql=SELECT TOP 100 * FROM AccountTrans
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

# JSON Stream — serialize rows client-side (mirrors JsonStream.razor)
GET {{baseUrl}}/sql/json-stream?sql=SELECT TOP 200 * FROM AccountTrans
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

# FOR JSON — server-side JSON (mirrors JsonStreamForjson.razor)
# SQL must include FOR JSON PATH or FOR JSON AUTO
GET {{baseUrl}}/sql/for-json?sql=SELECT TOP 200 * FROM Products FOR JSON PATH
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

# SQL — no token (expect 401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/sql/query?sql=SELECT TOP 10 * FROM sys.objects

###

### ─── HEALTH ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Health check (no token required)
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

###
